=9Cgenerate yield=E2=80=9D in  other crypto projects.[4] On the staking rew=
ards: Kwon endorsed=C2=A0this thread by Pedro Ojeda, which explains that if=
 you buy Luna and stake them you will get a nice yield on them paid by fees=
