emscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !=
important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-b=
ottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">is currently astronomical</a>,=
 because this is a risky but potentially rewarding trade. As Kwon and LFG a=
nd perhaps his capital partners rush to buy Terra to prop it up, other trad=
ers are rushing to sell it to blow it up.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px=
 0;">In good times, the algorithmic stablecoin essentially works because ev=
eryone wants to get rich. If everyone believes in the ecosystem, in the equ=
ity-like returns on the Luna token, in the stability of the Terra token, in=
 the interest rate on Terra, then it all works and they all=C2=A0<em>do=C2=
=A0</em>get rich. But once the peg breaks, the calculation changes. Now you=
 can get rich by betting on Luna if the peg recovers, but you can get rich =
by betting against it if it doesn=E2=80=99t. Everyone isn=E2=80=99t in it t=
ogether anymore, and it=E2=80=99s not clear which side will win.</p><table =
